sub_title: Partner of TwynstraGudde | Director of Bangladesh Delta Plan 2100 Formulation & Implementation Project | Strategic Advisor | Climate Adaptation and Governance Specialist | Manager Complex Projects
summary:
Experienced in research and consultancy related with strategy development and organizational change as well as with policy development and decision making. Especially focused on organizations or alliances dealing with complex developments and pressure.  
Related topics: water governance, cross cultural cooperation

Specialties: (diagnostic) research, coaching and advice, process consultation
